CDFglobalAttributes.PI_name: V. Angelopoulos, D. Larson & R.P. Lin, C.W. Carlson & J. McFadden
CDFglobalAttributes.TITLE: Ground Calculated Particle Moments (GMOM)
CDFglobalAttributes.TEXT: THEMIS-B:  Solid State Telescope (SST) & Electrostatic Analyzer (ESA): ground calculatedenergy fluxes & moments.(density, velocity, pressure, and temperature) Generated from ESA+SST combined distributions
CDFglobalAttributes.Logical_source_description: THEMIS-B:  Solid State Telescope (ESA+SST): Energy Flux spectrogram:  Data includes: Electron/Ion Ground-Calculated Fluxes (ions: 5 eV - 4 MeV,electrons: 6 eV - 700 keV)
